data.description: Beautifully maintained 5-bedroom home in an excellent school district, strategically situated near shopping centers, restaurants, and Northside Hospital. This meticulously cared-for residence boasts various upgrades, including new flooring, granite countertops, backsplash, and contemporary lighting fixtures. Enjoy the perfect blend of comfort and style in this spacious and well-appointed property. With its prime location and thoughtful enhancements, this home offers a wonderful living experience for you and your family. *Professional photos coming*
